 />\n又或者你講「呢個」就得，「呢家」就唔得，<br />\n咁就雙重標準了。"},{"pid":"217e1e4ac0b95caf59a6a26244d0d49034e840a4","tid":100920,"uid":77133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:00:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁大家會講「呢」個，定係「依」個？<br />\n如果你講「這一個」，咁你就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又或者你講「呢個」就得，「呢家」就唔得，<br />\n咁就雙重標準了。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個 同 而家 有咩矛盾<br />\n你會讀「而個」同「呢家」？<br />\n咁係咪反映懶音問題有啲嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定原來應該咁讀至啱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eecd4bd3fe97233dd046defb4e119d7e7da71b73","tid":100920,"uid":77133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宜家定而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼兩個都啱音先</blockquote><br />\n而家去宜家買宜家家儀"},{"pid":"684740b354674e863bb3984a487ef9ebf3a35c33","tid":100920,"uid":77133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>宜家定而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼兩個都啱音先</blockquote><br />\n而家去宜家買宜家家俬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n頂 未打完"},{"pid":"de6875b1f5cc3ab519f5a46375cc2236b45daa08","tid":100920,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:42:44.000Z","msg":"呢家都唔打得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n風紀啊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d085d32fa8d8145bf4ae47c70b537b041609f9","tid":100920,"uid":55634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T1