uote><blockquote>咁大家會講「呢」個，定係「依」個？<br />\n如果你講「這一個」，咁你就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又或者你講「呢個」就得，「呢家」就唔得，<br />\n咁就雙重標準了。</blockquote><br />\n照你咁講大家都會講「嗰」個，咁係咪都有「嗰」家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個、嗰個/果個<br />\n而家<br />\n<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f93fc2cfbf991919e000bc4fef6271d7141201","tid":100920,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T13:58:32.000Z","msg":"支持op<br />\n見到 「呢家」就打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4a39b91314d4df641ed61a686ab22079415bc6","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"依一刻、呢一刻都有人用，<br />\n而佢地都同樣可以用嚟表達「依家」。<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，有人會用「呢個」或者「依個」，<br />\n其實好睇佢地習慣。<br />\n<br />\n當然你要執到正都冇辦法，<br />\n一係你規範佢地要寫「在這一刻」，<br />\n唔準再用口語化文字。<br />\n<br />\n我本人非常支持正字，<br />\n但係今次似乎偏向用字習慣。<br />\n<br />\n利申：認真學術討論，非攻擊"},{"pid":"27f98e4f3287c533e640e110a8e9a007f0daa08a","tid":100920,"uid":36310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"一直都係依家 依排 <br />\n呢咩撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4e1d754bd5c6d2ea59091900af924fd500697b","tid":100920,"uid":36310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依一刻、呢一刻都有人用，<br />\n而佢地都同樣可以用嚟表達「依家」。<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，有人會用「呢個」或者「依個」，<br />\n其實好睇佢地習慣。<br />\n<br />\n當然你要執到正都冇辦法，<br />\n一係你規範佢地要寫「在這一刻」，<br />\n唔準再用口語化文字。<br />\n<br />\n我本人非常支持正字，<br />\n但係今次似乎偏向用字習慣。<br />\n<br />\n利申：認真學術討論，非攻擊</blockquote><br />\n你現實會發咩音?<br />\n真係讀呢(lee/nee)音?"},{"pid":"468788787b9d3c41284a330fd10d02a20b4a1bd6","tid":100920,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:08:55.000Z","msg":"好懷疑現實有冇人真係會講lee家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981fe0c3d3fcced2b24dfd9bad25b195d2a0e889","tid":100920,"uid":16120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:10:24.000Z","msg":"渣架"},{"pid":"0a563f4c107ffeab464a12bebf448c3eb26c56d0","tid":100920,"uid":2313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔打呢家咪打樓豬老母囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633864c779ddef452b23b9f24579f7857c5b4d29","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:15:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依一刻、呢一刻都有人用，<br />\n而佢地都同樣可以用嚟表達「依家」。<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，有人會用「呢個」或者「依個」，<br />\n其實好睇佢地習慣。<br />\n<br />\n當然你要執到正都冇辦法，<br />\n一係你規範佢地要寫「在這一刻」，<br />\n唔準再用口語化文字。<br />\n<br />\n我本人非常支持正字，<br />\n但係今次似乎偏向用字習慣。<br />\n<br />\n利申：認真學術討論，非攻擊</blockquote><br />\n你現實會發咩音?<br />\n真係讀呢(lee/nee)音?</blockquote><br />\n我自己用依家，但身邊兩種都有人用，<br />\n但佢哋係土生土長香港人。只係習慣問題。"},{"pid":"47a43e0eea191ca733c11abab8871a0debd20307","tid":100920,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:16:20.000Z","msg":"大陸人=呢家"},{"pid":"1d017eb387666e7c9054abbd70a8d6c3e8888cb4","tid":100920,"uid":9244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁大家會講「呢」個，定係「依」個？<br />\n如果你講「這一個」，咁你就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又或者你講「呢個」就得，「呢家」就唔得，<br />\n咁就雙重標準了。</blockquote><br />\n照你咁講大家都會講「嗰」個，咁係咪都有「嗰」家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9e935145450c4caca3e2536bb9156d21284a7d","tid":100920,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:17:08.000Z","msg":"咁呢家可以用咩呢"},{"pid":"0affe1c622058b869a032a257902444fc2895faa","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:18:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好懷疑現實有冇人真係會講lee家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我公司好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3523e5bd62a2db94dcf92affb3386ad3a56f6c","tid":100920,"uid":6313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:20:17.000Z","msg":"依家/宜家"},{"pid":"82a1ca2d8f4af8d0146c27d65fad9474f7675785","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸人=呢家</blockquote><br />\n其實世界並非只有黑與白。"},{"pid":"ad200a665a416c7c3f1878871010c27f4130bb1e","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"仲有，呢家=呢一刻係同義，相信大家唔會否應，反而，宜一刻、而一刻，可能小弟見識唔夠，真係未見過。"},{"pid":"4e651091fda0a4e8fd74e696ab9a2cfaedefbc1a","tid":100920,"uid":77754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依一刻、呢一刻都有人用，<br />\n而佢地都同樣可以用嚟表達「依家」。<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，有人會用「呢個」或者「依個」，<br />\n其實好睇佢地習慣。<br />\n<br />\n當然你要執到正都冇辦法，<br />\n一係你規範佢地要寫「在這一刻」，<br />\n唔準再用口語化文字。<br />\n<br />\n我本人非常支持正字，<br />\n但係今次似乎偏向用字習慣。<br />\n<br />\n利申：認真學術討論，非攻擊</blockquote><br />\n仲未識死 仲係到做呢個同依個做助證 喂大佬依家講緊依家 唔係依個定呢個 根本兩回事 更加唔關咩書面語定口語化事 問題係啲人將個呢字配個家字 但就算口語化你都唔會講lee家啦 亂咁用就當習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbdb796adb54719c54ac5d85d7d1ac07ce9e281","tid":100920,"uid":77754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有，呢家=呢一刻係同義，相信大家唔會否應，反而，宜一刻、而一刻，可能小弟見識唔夠，真係未見過。</blockquote><br />\n中文字唔係方程呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係咁樣sub落去㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   我上面都反問左你一次 咁嗰個=嗰一個 嗰家又等於咩呀咁 =嗰一刻 呀？ 咁你聽過人講嗰家未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8840bf553ad6e14017fcb503d6559fa3334dbd4","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:49:00.000Z","msg":"其實係咪必然要否定為先，討論為後？<br />\n定係我太認真呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都叫做幾詳細列明我論點，不過冇所謂，多言了！"},{"pid":"77be6895ece5e5574651b02b546b12d5a024b2f9","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有，呢家=呢一刻係同義，相信大家唔會否應，反而，宜一刻、而一刻，可能小弟見識唔夠，真係未見過。</blockquote><br />\n中文字唔係方程呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係咁樣sub落去㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   我上面都反問左你一次 咁嗰個=嗰一個 嗰家又等於咩呀咁 =嗰一刻 呀？ 咁你聽過人講嗰家未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰家：<br />\n例：嗰家，可以用嚟表達「某東西」、「某某舉動」，如果你得閒睇當年黑白片，嗰家真係有人用。"},{"pid":"f4005a5c81ccca24420859c96fa26da5ac346ddf","tid":100920,"uid":77754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪必然要否定為先，討論為後？<br />\n定係我太認真呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都叫做幾詳細列明我論點，不過冇所謂，多言了！</blockquote><br />\n我就係唔同意你嘅論點 咁我唔否定為先唔通肯定為先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   你列明得好詳細添 不過無視哂我所有反駁 冇討論過 所以都冇話咩討論為後 完。"},{"pid":"7cd3a5e1ba0471ca9447a99b475a90977c2397e4","tid":100920,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"Nigga 唔打ok?"},{"pid":"27b81c439aa3cbf8f6ab5ce59c5ac3fb99db6d3b","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有，呢家=呢一刻係同義，相信大家唔會否應，反而，宜一刻、而一刻，可能小弟見識唔夠，真係未見過。</blockquote><br />\n中文字唔係方程呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係咁樣sub落去㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   我上面都反問左你一次 咁嗰個=嗰一個 嗰家又等於咩呀咁 =嗰一刻 呀？ 咁你聽過人講嗰家未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當一方面閣下指出「中文字唔係方程式」，<br />\n而另一方面，你又要規範「呢家」同「依家」何謂正確。<br />\n其實上個網大家唔需要動氣，討論一下，對大家都有幫助！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59810124f09597862725047e59d5d09b1f680288","tid":100920,"uid":77754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:06:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有，呢家=呢一刻係同義，相信大家唔會否應，反而，宜一刻、而一刻，可能小弟見識唔夠，真係未見過。</blockquote><br />\n中文字唔係方程呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係咁樣sub落去㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   我上面都反問左你一次 咁嗰個=嗰一個 嗰家又等於咩呀咁 =嗰一刻 呀？ 咁你聽過人講嗰家未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰家：<br />\n例：嗰家，可以用嚟表達「某東西」、「某某舉動」，如果你得閒睇當年黑白片，嗰家真係有人用。</blockquote><br />\n咁你又話個家字係一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁你見過人話嗰一家代表嗰一刻未 但講到底呢家個呢字先係重點 唔好扯開"},{"pid":"dbbbbc6d09a7548554e5fd53f67ace18174a9c32","tid":100920,"uid":77754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有，呢家=呢一刻係同義，相信大家唔會否應，反而，宜一刻、而一刻，可能小弟見識唔夠，真係未見過。</blockquote><br />\n中文字唔係方程呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係咁樣sub落去㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   我上面都反問左你一次 咁嗰個=嗰一個 嗰家又等於咩呀咁 =嗰一刻 呀？ 咁你聽過人講嗰家未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當一方面閣下指出「中文字唔係方程式」，<br />\n而另一方面，你又要規範「呢家」同「依家」何謂正確。<br />\n其實上個網大家唔需要動氣，討論一下，對大家都有幫助！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n前者同後者個矛盾點係邊 中文的確唔係方程 但關規範個呢字嘅關係係邊？"},{"pid":"ad81a0cb517adcea0854a48e048baf6899a8cb69","tid":100920,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:10:52.000Z","msg":"正評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bc5c196f3082dffb9920768d12412398f1d2b8","tid":100920,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"呢字同個家放埋一齊我諗係得 呢家野 咁用<br />\n呢家野同lee家野可以互用<br />\n依家野都會咁講<br />\n但唔會有人講 而家野<br />\n<br />\n同理，依家同而家都有人講<br />\n但除非鄉音問題，我諗唔到點樣講到 呢家 或者 lee家<br />\n讀到lee家都算，當你讀開依家做lee家<br />\n但 呢家 我就真係唔知你點諗出嚟<br />\n<br />\n留意返，依/而/lee 三個字都算近音，但 呢 字真係大纜扯唔埋喎"},{"pid":"91a9210aec93d8f964e151abef9dd0a98829796d","tid":100920,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:38:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有，呢家=呢一刻係同義，相信大家唔會否應，反而，<span style=\"color: red;\">宜一刻、而一刻</span>，可能小弟見識唔夠，真係未見過。</blockquote><br />\n你自己已經答左自己啦<br />\n&ldquo;宜家&rdquo;&ldquo;而家&rdquo;啱，唔等如&ldquo;宜一刻&rdquo;&ldquo;而一刻&rdquo;啱<br />\n同樣地，唔係&ldquo;呢一刻&rdquo;啱就可以話&ldquo;呢家&rdquo;啱<br />\n所以你用有人用&ldquo;呢一刻&rdquo;黎支持 &ldquo;呢家&rdquo;嘅講法根本唔成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb975098a4eca3db6ad9a6f8942d9240084c0f6","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n中文字唔係方程呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係咁樣sub落去㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   我上面都反問左你一次 咁嗰個=嗰一個 嗰家又等於咩呀咁 =嗰一刻 呀？ 咁你聽過人講嗰家未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰家：<br />\n例：嗰家，可以用嚟表達「某東西」、「某某舉動」，如果你得閒睇當年黑白片，嗰家真係有人用。</blockquote><br />\n咁你又話個家字係一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁你見過人話嗰一家代表嗰一刻未 但講到底呢家個呢字先係重點 唔好扯開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來你對我初頭講嘅嘢有丁點誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我提到「呢個」，「呢家」，其實係想講「呢」一個字，其實係同樣地包含「這」嘅意思，而基於「呢家」=「呢一刻」都係指「這一刻」嘅道理，所以唔應該視之為錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n而「呢個」和「呢家」絕對沒有相同意思。"},{"pid":"e7fc6ad24880f527e7d37237f9e983a2deed33c6","tid":100920,"uid":20924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"點解英文可以有accent<br />\n但中文你地又咁執着一定要發嗰一個音？"},{"pid":"0a38dbc5ebae625c7545e4abd45d56c3830e4965","tid":100920,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n中文字唔係方程呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係咁樣sub落去㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   我上面都反問左你一次 咁嗰個=嗰一個 嗰家又等於咩呀咁 =嗰一刻 呀？ 咁你聽過人講嗰家未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰家：<br />\n例：嗰家，可以用嚟表達「某東西」、「某某舉動」，如果你得閒睇當年黑白片，嗰家真係有人用。</blockquote><br />\n咁你又話個家字係一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁你見過人話嗰一家代表嗰一刻未 但講到底呢家個呢字先係重點 唔好扯開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來你對我初頭講嘅嘢有丁點誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我提到「呢個」，「呢家」，其實係想講「呢」一個字，其實係同樣地包含「這」嘅意思，而基於「呢家」=「呢一刻」都係指「這一刻」嘅道理，所以唔應該視之為錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n而「呢個」和「呢家」絕對沒有相同意思。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote>仲有，呢家=呢一刻係同義，相信大家唔會否應，反而，<span style=\"color: red;\">宜一刻、而一刻</span>，可能小弟見識唔夠，真係未見過。</blockquote><br />\n你自己已經答左自己啦<br />\n&ldquo;宜家&rdquo;&ldquo;而家&rdquo;啱，唔等如&ldquo;宜一刻&rdquo;&ldquo;而一刻&rdquo;啱<br />\n同樣地，唔係&ldquo;呢一刻&rdquo;啱就可以話&ldquo;呢家&rdquo;啱<br />\n所以你用有人用&ldquo;呢一刻&rdquo;黎支持 &ldquo;呢家&rdquo;嘅講法根本唔成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b999b605d6f701c16d5ac915470d2585f5eccafc","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有，呢家=呢一刻係同義，相信大家唔會否應，反而，<span style=\"color: red;\">宜一刻、而一刻</span>，可能小弟見識唔夠，真係未見過。</blockquote><br />\n你自己已經答左自己啦<br />\n&ldquo;宜家&rdquo;&ldquo;而家&rdquo;啱，唔等如&ldquo;宜一刻&rdquo;&ldquo;而一刻&rdquo;啱<br />\n同樣地，唔係&ldquo;呢一刻&rdquo;啱就可以話&ldquo;呢家&rdquo;啱<br />\n所以你用有人用&ldquo;呢一刻&rdquo;黎支持 &ldquo;呢家&rdquo;嘅講法根本唔成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉，竟然寫錯別字：「否應」正確為 「否認」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外想問吓，「宜家」背後嘅出處？<br />\n反而「而家」二字，你可以引申為「而今」、「如今」等用詞。"},{"pid":"7df818b896782e2ec9156cc7d182ed7bb0bda5c0","tid":100920,"uid":77133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:57:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依一刻、呢一刻都有人用，<br />\n而佢地都同樣可以用嚟表達「依家」。<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，有人會用「呢個」或者「依個」，<br />\n其實好睇佢地習慣。<br />\n<br />\n當然你要執到正都冇辦法，<br />\n一係你規範佢地要寫「在這一刻」，<br />\n唔準再用口語化文字。<br />\n<br />\n我本人非常支持正字，<br />\n但係今次似乎偏向用字習慣。<br />\n<br />\n利申：認真學術討論，非攻擊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得「而家」可以表達「呢一刻」嘅意思<br />\n不過呢一刻=/=而家<br />\n例如話：<br />\n我而家每日見到呢家，我而家忍唔住想講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上嘅「而家」係唔可以用「呢一刻」代替<br />\n因為「呢一刻」只係「一剎那」咁解<br />\n而「而家」嘅定義就大好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁......咩係呢家呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a3f7bae9b5eecf0aefd068fe7d00b00f59ff07","tid":100920,"uid":77754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n嗰家：<br />\n例：嗰家，可以用嚟表達「某東西」、「某某舉動」，如果你得閒睇當年黑白片，嗰家真係有人用。</blockquote><br />\n咁你又話個家字係一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁你見過人話嗰一家代表嗰一刻未 但講到底呢家個呢字先係重點 唔好扯開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來你對我初頭講嘅嘢有丁點誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我提到「呢個」，「呢家」，其實係想講「呢」一個字，其實係同樣地包含「這」嘅意思，而基於「呢家」=「呢一刻」都係指「這一刻」嘅道理，所以唔應該視之為錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n而「呢個」和「呢家」絕對沒有相同意思。</blockquote><br />\nok 你話個呢字有這意思都仲可以接受 但「依家」其實係由而今變成 你自己上網都可以睇到 而家字係由今字脫m音變成 所以本來就係一個詞  所以你可以話呢一刻 但呢家就點都講唔通  <br />\n回埋樓上，有時唔係執唔執著於一個音 一個音錯左影響到字義本身的話 就由得佢當算數 唔通咁先叫唔執著 叫豁達？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7d75922567d366a6b0a9650c185202198d283e","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解英文可以有accent<br />\n但中文你地又咁執着一定要發嗰一個音？</blockquote><br />\n書寫口語化嘅錯！"},{"pid":"7da9c0515a93b125f68ecb9256f7826cb84688f7","tid":100920,"uid":77754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:05:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有，呢家=呢一刻係同義，相信大家唔會否應，反而，<span style=\"color: red;\">宜一刻、而一刻</span>，可能小弟見識唔夠，真係未見過。</blockquote><br />\n你自己已經答左自己啦<br />\n&ldquo;宜家&rdquo;&ldquo;而家&rdquo;啱，唔等如&ldquo;宜一刻&rdquo;&ldquo;而一刻&rdquo;啱<br />\n同樣地，唔係&ldquo;呢一刻&rdquo;啱就可以話&ldquo;呢家&rdquo;啱<br />\n所以你用有人用&ldquo;呢一刻&rdquo;黎支持 &ldquo;呢家&rdquo;嘅講法根本唔成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉，竟然寫錯別字：「否應」正確為 「否認」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外想問吓，「宜家」背後嘅出處？<br />\n反而「而家」二字，你可以引申為「而今」、「如今」等用詞。</blockquote><br />\n宜家 依家 呢啲就係近音字同音字啦 但呢字嘅字音真係不能令人接受 非常奇怪"},{"pid":"88a76b8f8f73ecb2f70fb16a9928f466aa593cf5","tid":100920,"uid":77133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解英文可以有accent<br />\n但中文你地又咁執着一定要發嗰一個音？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n口音上，一個字可能有幾個音<br />\n但唔包懶音<br />\n咁以後仲洗唔洗學發音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起鴨脷洲口音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab92b5964e257bd37cfcf61fa24ba2f70764a664","tid":100920,"uid":35040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"呢家好明顯自己講得/聽得懶音鄉音多<br />\n正音依家、宜家，講呢家真係柒到"},{"pid":"b194979a78ef1d149ffc0f642633e875c67fa2ed","tid":100920,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:10:18.000Z","msg":"「呢家」呢啲真係柒到喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6185952e6bdaa000d4a56c90c2d93bc35d67aabc","tid":100920,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"「呢家」依兩個字真係好少見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79af752b3543b896848a029c8279dd6d00461b7","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:14:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依一刻、呢一刻都有人用，<br />\n而佢地都同樣可以用嚟表達「依家」。<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，有人會用「呢個」或者「依個」，<br />\n其實好睇佢地習慣。<br />\n<br />\n當然你要執到正都冇辦法，<br />\n一係你規範佢地要寫「在這一刻」，<br />\n唔準再用口語化文字。<br />\n<br />\n我本人非常支持正字，<br />\n但係今次似乎偏向用字習慣。<br />\n<br />\n利申：認真學術討論，非攻擊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得「而家」可以表達「呢一刻」嘅意思<br />\n不過呢一刻=/=而家<br />\n例如話：<br />\n我而家每日見到呢家，我而家忍唔住想講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上嘅「而家」係唔可以用「呢一刻」代替<br />\n因為「呢一刻」只係「一剎那」咁解<br />\n而「而家」嘅定義就大好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁......咩係呢家呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所言甚是！突然一言驚醒，「而家」仲有輔助性，例如：而/依家呢一刻我好開心有人認真討論！<br />\n<br />\n「而家」可用作加強語氣！<br />\n而家呢一刻我好鍾意妳，咁下一刻呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而「呢家」嘛，就係口語咁簡單！"},{"pid":"90eb81ee9433b04209ded2b339363d64e1ad5f11","tid":100920,"uid":67231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:15:21.000Z","msg":"講「呢家」真係係好柒<br />\n但我又唔好意思話你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae12898026b5040ce67ab7610f0b3a12b9d0f59","tid":100920,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:19:16.000Z","msg":"E+"},{"pid":"57ab5882d34449df33199611ca97bb71b9dd6855","tid":100920,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"有鄉音仲以為自己冇錯<br />\n當你譚仔呀姐喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6c1ddef93e5a945164d80668d7071fd34dff01","tid":100920,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"宜/依/而 或 呢 嘅本字有人話係 「爾」<br />\n而 「爾」文言文入面的確有 「這 , 此」嘅意思，用法同廣東話一樣<br />\n<br />\n如果「爾」真係本字嘅話，咁兩種讀法都啱<br />\n「爾」字讀已，「彌」字就變咗做「尼」<br />\n<br />\n有人讀宜/依/而，有人讀尼好可能就係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6847001e0c4abd5f0b2ef55c9762a99ee0f06851","tid":100920,"uid":77133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依一刻、呢一刻都有人用，<br />\n而佢地都同樣可以用嚟表達「依家」。<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，有人會用「呢個」或者「依個」，<br />\n其實好睇佢地習慣。<br />\n<br />\n當然你要執到正都冇辦法，<br />\n一係你規範佢地要寫「在這一刻」，<br />\n唔準再用口語化文字。<br />\n<br />\n我本人非常支持正字，<br />\n但係今次似乎偏向用字習慣。<br />\n<br />\n利申：認真學術討論，非攻擊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得「而家」可以表達「呢一刻」嘅意思<br />\n不過呢一刻=/=而家<br />\n例如話：<br />\n我而家每日見到呢家，我而家忍唔住想講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上嘅「而家」係唔可以用「呢一刻」代替<br />\n因為「呢一刻」只係「一剎那」咁解<br />\n而「而家」嘅定義就大好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁......咩係呢家呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所言甚是！突然一言驚醒，「而家」仲有輔助性，例如：而/依家呢一刻我好開心有人認真討論！<br />\n<br />\n「而家」可用作加強語氣！<br />\n而家呢一刻我好鍾意妳，咁下一刻呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而「呢家」嘛，就係口語咁簡單！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我呢家同你趕，許只係口音唔正<br />\n我手寫我口音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4dbb1bf650bf8bb463011bd7c8dc06d652afd1","tid":100920,"uid":13130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:24:05.000Z","msg":"非洲土語 你好咁解"},{"pid":"22778abe83a8ff7c109e4e9b0de61a824f9a6c14","tid":100920,"uid":2961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:24:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\nok 你話個呢字有這意思都仲可以接受 但「依家」其實係由而今變成 你自己上網都可以睇到 而家字係由今字脫m音變成 所以本來就係一個詞  所以你可以話呢一刻 但呢家就點都講唔通  <br />\n回埋樓上，有時唔係執唔執著於一個音 一個音錯左影響到字義本身的話 就由得佢當算數 唔通咁先叫唔執著 叫豁達？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到尾，其實大家都係想保衞香港人嘅廣東話，<br />\n我絶對明白你意思。<br />\n有陣時，同我兩位外甥講嘢，真係好勞氣！<br />\n唯有叫佢地睇多啲書，查多啲字典，而唔係單睇報紙、雜誌！"},{"pid":"499f25443d2e43f2a4504e2a8a9e6b38ceec6c49","tid":100920,"uid":54755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:27:37.000Z","msg":"未睇呢個post之前都唔信有人會打呢家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚怪"},{"pid":"9ce8122ead86e9f9296514569ccf26ed30ae8e93","tid":100920,"uid":37820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"好似原詞係「而今」，但讀讀下變而家"},{"pid":"b7d23c1c6f731f0b9dfbbae583728d13fd7fee30","tid":100920,"uid":77133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:33:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜/依/而 或 呢 嘅本字有人話係 「爾」<br />\n而 「爾」文言文入面的確有 「這 , 此」嘅意思，用法同廣東話一樣<br />\n<br />\n如果「爾」真係本字嘅話，咁兩種讀法都啱<br />\n「爾」字讀已，「彌」字就變咗做「尼」<br />\n<br />\n有人讀宜/依/而，有人讀尼好可能就係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係以前啲人睇少咗個部首？<br />\n好似希臘讀咗希獵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}